%%{init: {"theme": "neutral"} }%%
flowchart TD
    Start([Visitor lands on Bookmi]) --> Choice{Sign up method}
    Choice -- email --> EmailSignup[Enter email + password]
    Choice -- OAuth --> OAuth[OAuth provider redirect]

    EmailSignup --> OTP[Verify email OTP]
    OAuth --> Callback["/auth/callback (Supabase PKCE)"]
    Callback --> Session[Session established]
    OTP --> Session

    Session --> Gate{"host_profiles row<br/>exists? (RequireAuth)"}
    Gate -- no --> Wizard[Onboarding wizard]
    Gate -- yes --> Dashboard

    subgraph Wizard [Onboarding wizard - single screen]
        direction TB
        W1[Enter display name] --> W2[Auto-generated slug<br/>editable, live availability check]
        W2 --> W3[Upload avatar<br/>Cloudinary, optional]
        W3 --> W4["POST /hosts/me/profile"]
    end

    W4 --> Dashboard[Redirect to dashboard]
    Dashboard --> FirstService[Add first service<br/>booking or tip type]
    FirstService --> Share[Share storefront link]
    Share --> PayoutLater["(later, opt-in from<br/>Profile > Payout section)<br/>add bank account +<br/>BVN / reserved account"]

    style Wizard fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#999
